query:
SELECT 
	--Keys
	m.mbr_indv_be_key,
	left(c.CLM_SVC_STRT_DT_SK, 7) "Service Date", 
	left(c.clm_rcvd_dt_sk, 7) "Received Date",
	c.DIAG_CD_1_SK,
	c.NDC_SK,
	cl.CLM_LN_PROC_CD_SK,
	c.DIAG_CD_1_SK,
	c.DIAG_CD_2_SK,
	c.DIAG_CD_3_SK,
	c.PROC_CD_1_SK,
	c.PROC_CD_2_SK,
	c.PROC_CD_3_SK,
	--Claim Types
	c.CLM_TYP_CD "Claim Type lvl 1",
	c.CLM_SUBTYP_CD "Claim Type lvl 2",
	cl.DNTL_CLM_LN_DNTL_CAT_CD "Dental Category Code",
	c.DIAG_CD_CAT_CD "Diagnosis Type",
	cl.clm_ln_pos_cd,
	--Potential Filters
	c.SRC_SYS_CD, 
	c.FUND_CAT_CD,
	c.SRC_SYS_CD,
	c.CLM_FINL_DISP_CD,
	--g.GRP_MKT_SIZE_CAT_CD,
	--Drug Info
	c.DRUG_CLM_TIER_CD,
	c.DRUG_CLM_SPEC_DRUG_IN "SpecialtyIndicator",
	c.DRUG_CLM_GNRC_DRUG_IN "GenericIndicator",
	c.DRUG_CLM_MAIL_ORDER_IN "MailOrder",
	--Payment Info
  (c.CLM_LN_TOT_PAYBL_AMT - c.CLM_LN_TOT_PAYBL_TO_PROV_AMT) "MemberPay",
	c.DRUG_CLM_INGR_CST_ALW_AMT "IngredientCost",
	c.DRUG_CLM_UCR_AMT "RetailCost"

FROM 
	PROD.CLM_F c 
	--JOIN 
	--	PROD.CLM_F2 c2 on c2.CLM_SK = c.CLM_SK
	inner JOIN 
		PROD.CLM_LN_F cl ON cl.CLM_SK = c.CLM_SK
	--JOIN 
	--	PROD.GRP_D g ON g.GRP_SK = c.GRP_SK
	inner join
		prod.mbr_d m on m.mbr_sk = c.mbr_sk
	--left join 
	--	NDC_D ND on ND.NDC_SK = c.NDC_SK
	--left join 
	--	DRUG_CLM_PRICE_F DCPF on DCPF.CLM_ID = C.CLM_ID

WHERE   
	c.CLM_CAT_CD='STD' 
	--AND c.CLM_FINL_DISP_CD='ACPTD' 
	AND c.CLM_STTUS_CD in ('A02','A08','A09') 
--AND CLM_F.CLM_TYP_CD='MED' 
--AND CLM_F.SRC_SYS_CD in ('ESI','OPTUMRX' ,'FACETS')
	--and cl.PROD_SH_NM in ('PCB', 'BCARE', 'BLUE-SELECT', 'BLUESELECT+', 'BLUE-ACCESS', 'PC', 'PCBEXTRNL') 
--AND GRP_D.GRP_MKT_SIZE_CAT_CD in ('LGGRP1', 'LGGRP2', 'LGGRP3', 'MDGRP1', 'MDGRP2', 'SMGRP2', 'SMGRP1', 'MCARE', 'MCAREDRPAY', 'MCAREGRP', 'ASO', 'DP') 
	AND c.clm_svc_strt_dt_sk >= char(current date - 49 month, iso)
	and c.clm_pd_dt_sk >= char(current date - 49 month, iso)
	AND c.clm_svc_strt_dt_sk < char(current date, iso)
	and c.clm_pd_dt_sk < char(current date, iso)
	and c.prod_sh_nm not in ('BMADVH','BMADVP','CBLU65','DENTMA','MEDGAP','MEDSEL','THC65','TIP')
	and M.MBR_BRTH_DT_SK <= CHAR(current date - 650 Months, ISO)
